== Coping with Designing Problems ==
Many problems with modeling in 3D come from poor practice early on in the creation of your project. These kinds of problems can be difficult to rectify later on without completely recreating the project. This chapter will help you deal with these problems before they occur. Navigate to the next page to start the chapter.<br>
