== Recommendation on vocabulary == 

I think the items in the table below should be added to the article, although I haven't yet collected their translations (and the list is not yet complete).  --[[User:Sigma 7|Sigma 7]] ([[User talk:Sigma 7|talk]]) 16:54, 23 March 2009 (UTC)

=== Vocab table ===

{{col-begin}}
{{col-3}}
*Airplane - l'avion (m)
*Airport -  l'aéroport (m)
*Boat - le bateau
*Bus - l'autobus (m)
*Car - l'auto (f)
*Station - la station
*Train - le train
{{col-3}}
*Cruise - la croisière (is this correct?)
*Ticket - le billet
*Tour - le tour
*Reservation - la réserve (might not be used in travel context)
*Resort - une station (doubtful)
*Vacation - les vacances (f)
{{col-3}}
*Departure
*Arrival
*Passenger

{{col-end}}

