This book is intended to serve as a guide for those who are switching to Windows for the first time, and making the move from OS X to Windows 7.  For this book, we will assume you are already using OS X 10.5.  We will highlight the differences between the two operating systems, and provide helpful comparisons in how to get things done in Windows 7.

Please enjoy this guide, and enjoy your new operating system!

